{"_path":"/maps/_ai/operations/distributed","_dir":"operations","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Distributed Training","description":"分布式训练技术与框架，包括 DeepSpeed、FSDP、Megatron-Core 等大规模模型训练方案。","original_path":"_ai/distributed.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"分布式-distributed-training"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分布式 (Distributed Training)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"deepspeedzero-优化器的显存革命"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSpeed：ZeRO 优化器的显存革命"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSpeed 是微软开源的深度学习优化库，核心是 ZeRO（Zero Redundancy Optimizer）技术。通过三个阶段逐步释放显存压力：ZeRO-1 优化器状态分片节省 4x 显存，ZeRO-2 梯度分片再节省 2x，ZeRO-3 参数分片再节省 2x 并支持单卡加载超大模型。它是训练 100B+ 参数模型的首选方案，支持流水线并行、张量并行与 ZeRO 的组合。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/deepspeedai/DeepSpeed","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSpeed GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/zero-deepspeed-new-system-optimizations-enable-training-models-with-over-100-billion-parameters/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ZeRO 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.deepspeed.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSpeed 官网"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"fsdppytorch-原生全分片数据并行"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FSDP：PyTorch 原生全分片数据并行"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FSDP（Fully Sharded Data Parallel）是 PyTorch 官方的大模型分布式方案，设计理念与 DeepSpeed ZeRO-3 类似，但集成更紧密。它将模型参数、梯度和优化器状态分片到多个 GPU 上，在保持通信开销不变的同时显著降低单卡内存占用。API 简洁，与 PyTorch 生态无缝集成，适合快速迭代的研究场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.pytorch.org/tutorials/intermediate/FSDP_advanced_tutorial.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PyTorch FSDP 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://pytorch.org/blog/introducing-pytorch-fully-sharded-data-parallel-api/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FSDP 介绍"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/accelerate/en/concept_guides/fsdp_and_deepspeed","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FSDP vs DeepSpeed 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"megatron-core万亿参数模型的训练框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Megatron-Core：万亿参数模型的训练框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Megatron-Core 是 NVIDIA 专为万亿参数模型设计的训练框架，提供张量并行（层内切分，适合单节点多卡）、流水线并行（层间切分，适合多节点）、序列并行（长序列场景降低激活显存）的原生实现。通过 8 路张量并行和 8 路流水线并行，可在 1024 张 A100 上训练 175B 参数的 GPT-3 模型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/NVIDIA/Megatron-LM","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Megatron-LM GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.nvidia.com/megatron-core/developer-guide/latest/user-guide/parallelism-guide.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Megatron 并行策略指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/scaling-language-model-training-to-a-trillion-parameters-using-megatron/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"万亿参数训练"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"acceleratehugging-face-分布式封装"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accelerate：Hugging Face 分布式封装"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accelerate 是 Hugging Face 提供的分布式训练封装库，让单卡代码几乎零改动扩展到多卡/多机。只需几行代码即可完成模型、优化器、数据加载器的分布式准备。支持 DeepSpeed、FSDP、Megatron 等多种后端，提供统一的配置界面，是研究实验快速迭代的利器。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/accelerate/index","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accelerate 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/huggingface/accelerate","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accelerate GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"分布式训练选择指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分布式训练选择指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模型规模决定并行策略：< 7B 单卡或 DDP 足够，7B-70B 使用 FSDP 或 DeepSpeed ZeRO-3，70B+ 需要 Megatron-Core 配合多种并行组合。场景偏好：研究/实验推荐 Accelerate + FSDP 快速迭代，生产部署选择 DeepSpeed 功能全面，超大规模训练使用 Megatron-Core 配合 NVIDIA 优化。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sumanthrh.com/post/distributed-and-efficient-finetuning/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分布式训练完整指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://llamafactory.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced/distributed.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaMA-Factory 分布式"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"deepspeedzero-优化器的显存革命","depth":2,"text":"DeepSpeed：ZeRO 优化器的显存革命"},{"id":"fsdppytorch-原生全分片数据并行","depth":2,"text":"FSDP：PyTorch 原生全分片数据并行"},{"id":"megatron-core万亿参数模型的训练框架","depth":2,"text":"Megatron-Core：万亿参数模型的训练框架"},{"id":"acceleratehugging-face-分布式封装","depth":2,"text":"Accelerate：Hugging Face 分布式封装"},{"id":"分布式训练选择指南","depth":2,"text":"分布式训练选择指南"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:operations:distributed.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/operations/distributed.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/operations/distributed","_extension":"md"}